reviewText: The laughs were good, but a bit too predictable. I'm going back to the originals - Monty Python's Flying Circus.
Falling off your chair funny -- every time.  Also much information about the making of the original series.

John Cleese  is superbly hilarious. I bought this for my husband for Christmas and he loved it. We seen all 0f the series and even sat down with our 9 year old granddaughter, who I thought was going to roll off the couch. We seen them in 1975 but wanted our own collection. Great work John Cleese!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
